fields.name: Barbarian
fields.description: A savage berserker focusing their rage into offensive strikes and constitution bolstering manuevers.

fields.name: Bard
fields.description: Charismatic to a point, bards use their silvertongues and musical aptitude to control the battlefield and help their allies.

fields.name: Cleric
fields.description: A devout follower of their faith that harnesses their dieties energies to help their allies or dispatch their foes.

fields.name: Druid
fields.description: A gifted shapeshifter and practitioner of nature magic. Well rounded and diverse druids can fill just about any party role.

fields.name: Fighter
fields.description: A master of combat their uses their martial prowess to bolster themselves agaisnt damage or focus their might into tactical strikes.

fields.name: Monk
fields.description: Skilled in the martial arts and the use of their Ki. Allowing for multiple stikes and evasive manuevers.

fields.name: Paladin
fields.description: A warrior of the faith. Take your Oath and use the magical power to aid yourself on your crusade.

fields.name: Ranger
fields.description: A skilled marksman with extensive knowledge of the wilds. Aid your party at range with a flurry of arrows or an animal companion.

fields.name: Rogue
fields.description: A master of stealth that prefers trickery and flanking to head-to-head comabat. Master of sleight of hand and theivery.

fields.name: Sorcerer
fields.description: A sorcerer is attuned to magic through their bloodline. Allowing for a natural aptitude to bend magic to their will.

fields.name: Warlock
fields.description: A warlock derives their powers their pacts made with Eldritch beings. Masters of control through manipulation and blasts of energy.

fields.name: Wizard
fields.description: A wizard is attuned to magic through rigorous study. A master of their craft they learn can cast spells of great magnitude. Highly verstile magic.
